divs: Sighting DetailsThese clouds were in front of me as I drove West towards Fresno, Cal. Pictures were taken by my passenger at my request...Reviewing the pictures later I noticed things I had not seen or realised at first. Not only does the large cloud have what appears to be a swirling extension vapor trail like swirl benieth it...but the other two clouds have circular swirls in thier center and...in upper right of large cloud in one of the photos there is a shiny translucent disc shaped object that is at an angle tipping into the cloud. Wanted your opinions. I have a few more pictures of the same...some through the windshield and some from out the window
Summary: Saw these clouds as I was driving towards Fresno and had my passenger take the pictures
